 BTS 的 Jungkook 放弃了《Seven》的两首新混音版https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-solo-7-summer-band-remix-release-3469232?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=bts-jungkook-solo-7-summer-band-混音发行Gladys YeoMon, 17 Jul 2023 06:25:58 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3469232 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="防弹少年团柾国七评论" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他们的标题是“Summer Mix”和“Band Ver”</p><p>防弹<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-solo-seven-summer-band-remix-release-3469232">少年团 (BTS) 的柾国 (Jungkook) 发布了《Seven》的两首新混音版，</a>首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="防弹少年团柾国七评论" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/jungkook-seven-review-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bts">BTS</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungkook">Jungkook</a>发布了他最近的单曲“Seven”的两个新版本。</p><ul><li class="p1"><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/bts-jungkook-seven-review-solo-era-uk-garage-3468564">在《七》中，防弹少年团的柾国在英国车库的夏日高潮中开启了他的个人生涯</a></strong></li></ul><p>7 月 17 日，这位韩国流行歌手推出了与美国说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/latto">Latto</a>合作的新单曲“Seven”的 Summer 和 Band 混音版。该曲目的两个新版本现已在 YouTube 和流媒体服务上提供。</p><p> “夏季混音”以爵士乐独奏开始，并以更加繁忙、舞蹈为主的器乐为特色。与此同时，“Band Ver”强调了曲目的原声吉他并换成了更传统的鼓节奏。下面听听他们的声音。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="정국 (Jung Kook) &#39;Seven (feat. Latto) - Summer Mix&#39; Visualizer" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vn4GNjIotSM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="七 (feat. Latto) - 乐队版本。" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zj0O6-YvLhg?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 《七》最初于上周五（7 月 14 日）与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-solo-single-seven-3463264">韩国女演员韩素熙 (Han So-hee) 主演的音乐视频</a>一起发布。 Big Hit Music 还将其发行称为 Jungkook 个人活动的正式开始，暗示 BTS 歌手将推出更多音乐。</p><p>在对这首单曲的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/track/bts-jungkook-seven-review-solo-era-uk-garage-3468564">四星评论</a>中， <em>《NME</em> 》的瑞安·戴利 (Rhian Daly) 称《七》是“一款适合夏季的波普音乐，也为歌手的艺术才华增添了新的方面”，并赞扬了拉托在这首歌中“毫不费力”的特点。</p><p>虽然《Seven》标志着田柾国作为独唱者的正式首秀，但这位偶像此前已经推出了多首个人歌曲，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-music-video-2022-fifa-world-cup-soundtrack-single-dreamers-3354194">2022 年 FIFA 世界杯的《Dreamers》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-shares-heartfelt-new-song-my-you-3245144">BTS 2022 Festa 的《My You》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-suga-stay-alive-7fates-chakho-soundtrack-3159452"><i>7Fates 的《Stay Alive》：查科</i>原声带</a>。</p><p>在发行《Seven》之前，柾国制作了两首较早的独唱歌曲《Still With You》和《My You》， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-still-with-you-my-you-spotify-apple-3463963">并首次在流媒体服务上提供</a>。这首歌最初分别于 2022 年和 2020 年发行，作为 BTS 年度 Festa 庆祝活动的一部分。</p><p>防弹<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bts-jungkook-solo-seven-summer-band-remix-release-3469232">少年团 (BTS) 的柾国 (Jungkook) 发布了《Seven》的两首新混音版，</a>首先在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上出现。</p> ;
